OL,3,CPope has 'peaceful night' after
OL,4,Crespiratory crisis and blood
OL,5,Ctransfusion
OL,7,FPope Francis had a "peaceful night"
OL,8,Fand is now resting following a
OL,9,Frespiratory crisis and blood
OL,10,Ftransfusions, the Vatican said on
OL,11,FSunday.
OL,13,FVatican spokesman Matteo Bruni's one-
OL,14,Fline statement didn't mention if
OL,15,FFrancis was up or eating breakfast.
OL,17,FThe brief update came after doctors
OL,18,Fsaid the 88-year-old pope, who had
OL,19,Fpart of one lung removed as a young
OL,20,Fman, was in critical condition.
