OL,3,CPope has 'peaceful night' after
OL,4,Crespiratory crisis and blood
OL,5,Ctransfusion
OL,7,FThe pope received "high flows" of
OL,8,Foxygen to help him breathe. He also
OL,9,Freceived blood transfusions after
OL,10,Ftests showed low counts of platelets,
OL,11,Fwhich are needed for clotting, the
OL,12,FVatican said in a late update.
OL,14,FThe Saturday statement also said that
OL,15,Fthe pontiff "continues to be alert and
OL,16,Fspent the day in an armchair although
OL,17,Fin more pain than yesterday." Doctors
OL,18,Fsaid the prognosis was "reserved".
