OL,3,CPope has 'peaceful night' after
OL,4,Crespiratory crisis and blood
OL,5,Ctransfusion
OL,7,F"The Holy Father continues to be alert
OL,8,Fand spent the day in an armchair
OL,9,Falthough in more pain than yesterday,"
OL,10,Fthe previous statement said. "At the
OL,11,Fmoment the prognosis is reserved," the
OL,12,Fstatement said.
OL,14,FDoctors have said Francis' condition
OL,15,Fis touch-and-go, given his age,
OL,16,Ffragility and pre-existing lung
OL,17,Fdisease, and that the main threat
OL,18,Ffacing him is if the infection enters
OL,19,Fthe bloodstream, a serious condition
OL,20,Fknown as sepsis.
